  <head>
    <title>Waffle Recipe</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="recipe">
      <h3>Waffle Recipe</h3>
      <h6>Dry Ingredients</h6>
        <ul>
          <li>1 c. flour</li>
          <li>1 tbsp baking powder</li>
        </ul>
      <h6>Wet Ingredients</h6>
        <ul>
          <li>1 eggs</li>
          <li>2 tbsp. sugar</li>
          <li>2 tbsp. butter</li>
          <li>1 c. milk</li>
        </ul>
      <h6>Intructions</h6>
        <ol>
          <li>Combine dry ingredients, set aside.</li>
          <li>Separate egg yolk and egg white.</li>
          <li>Combine egg yolk, butter, and milk, mix with dry ingredients.</li>
          <li>Beat egg whites to stiff peaks, gradually adding sugar after 30s until fully incorporated.</li>
          <li>Fold egg whites into batter.</li>
          <li>Cook in waffle iron (approx. 1/3 c. batter per waffle)</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
  </body>
</html
